ote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/7UUAKQxiayI7DnBzhbngayzpGXG.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T06:39:42.132+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":113,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Rita, who finds herself alone when husband Ariel works abroad. They both find solace and sexual satisfaction in other people. When Ariel comes back, they both act like nothing happened. But will this keep their marriage from falling apart?"},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"丽塔","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"当丈夫阿列尔（Ariel）在国外工作时，丽塔（Rita）发现自己独自一人非常寂寞。 他们都在其他人身上找到安慰和性满足。 阿列尔回来时，他们都表现得好像什么都没发生过。 但这样能防止他们的婚姻破裂吗？"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Tân Nương Khát Tình","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Tân nương Rita thấy cô đơn khi chồng Ariel đi làm ở nước ngoài. Cả hai đều tìm thấy sự thỏa mãn tình dục ở người khác. Khi Ariel quay lại, cả hai đều làm như không có chuyện gì xảy ra. Nhưng liệu điều này có giúp cuộc hôn nhân của họ không tan vỡ?"},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Rita, die alleen is als echtgenoot Ariel in het buitenland werkt. Ze vinden allebei troost en seksuele bevrediging bij andere mensen. Als Ariel terugkomt, doen ze allebei alsof er niets is gebeurd. Maar zal dit voorkomen dat hun huwelijk uiteenvalt?"},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ariel dela v tujini, njegova žena Rita je doma sama. Uteho in spolno zadovoljstvo oba najdeta v drugih ljudeh. Ko se Ariel vrne, se obnašata, kot da se ni nič zgodilo. Toda ali bo to zadoščalo, da prepreči razpad njunega zakona?"},"name":"Slovenščina","iso_639_1":"sl","iso_3166_1":"SI","english_name":"Slovenian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Rita se regăsește singură atunci când soțul ei, Ariel, lucrează în străinătate. Amândoi își găsesc alinarea și satisfacția sexuală alături de alte persoane. Când Ariel se întoarce, amândoi se comportă ca și cum nimic nu s-ar fi întâmplat. Dar va reuși acest lucru să le mențină căsnicia?"},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"홀로 남은 아내: 리타","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"해외로 떠난 남편을 기다리며 홀로 남겨진 리타. 끝없는 외로움은 그녀를 서서히 다른 사람의 품으로 이끌고, 남편 역시 타국에서 비밀스러운 위안을 찾는다. 재회한 두 사람은 아무 일도 없었던 듯 일상을 이어가려 하는데, 둘의 결혼은 결국 파국을 맞는다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":11845,"adult":false,"title":"Intimacy","video":false,"overview":"Failed musician Jay abandoned his family and now earns a living as head bartender in a trendy London pub. Every Wednesday afternoon, a woman comes to his house for graphic, almost wordless, sex. One day, Jay follows her and learns about her. This eventually disrupts their relationship.","genre_ids":[10749,18,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.5807,"vote_count":545,"poster_path":"/aiPhBVo2eNhuPw5Pezx4BHagvUx.jpg","release_date":"2001-01-20","vote_average":6.226,"backdrop_path":"/qoxriJ6n1qxvG1bBMPnsZBHKGco.jpg","original_title":"Intimacy","original_language":"en"},{"id":592695,"adult":false,"title":"Pleasure","video":false,"overview":"19 year old Linnéa leaves her small town in Sweden and heads for Los Angeles with the aim of becoming the world's next big porn star, but the road to her goal turns out to be bumpier than she imagined.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.176,"vote_count":761,"poster_path":"/TcOsu6iO5prSJbDn9oIQgIW655.jpg","release_date":"2021-10-08","vote_average":6.281,"backdrop_path":"/y0LhmaMYpFkIfrUlOpJYTVMH2eA.jpg","original_title":"Pleasure","original_language":"sv"},{"id":74555,"adult":false,"title":"Evil Things","video":false,"overview":"On January 9, 2009, five college students left New York City for a weekend in the country. 48 hours later, all five students have simply vanished without a trace. There were no leads and no evidence - until now.","genre_ids":[27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2787,"vote_count":61,"poster_path":"/t5J2PIAudfPaHMuAgs9tc29vbEo.jpg","release_date":"2009-06-17","vote_average":4.533,"backdrop_path":"/llpUbyitPOFRBwhXjfsr3wv59tR.jpg","original_title":"Evil Things","original_language":"en"},{"id":1196632,"adult":false,"title":"Salakab","video":false,"overview":"Lena returns to her hometown after finishing college. Her boyfriend Arthur is consumed with jealousy and fury upon learning that Lena has another boyfriend from the city.","genre_ids":[53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.4947,"vote_count":7,"poster_path":"/iv6RPn35qbMp2NImO76QNepBcS4.jpg","release_date":"2023-11-17","vote_average":4.6,"backdrop_path":"/obz2rAWVhBXKr1pG2DwjZmA30nJ.jpg","original_title":"Salakab","original_language":"tl"},{"id":1137010,"adult":false,"title":"R","video":false,"overview":"In Los Angeles in 1965, unfulfilled B-list director Gordon Flemyng (Brad Pollak) receives the screenplay of a lifetime from his old friend Robert Sabaroff (Mark Baker), who is insistent they make a film that promises to entertain like no other. With football legend, turned actor, Jim Brown (J'amore Ward) attached to the picture, it seems the sky's the limit for these two filmmakers. Desperate to finally receive the recognition he's longed for, Gordon struggles to find the balance between passion and stardom. However, when Gordon pushes the MPAA rating guidelines of traditional cinema, he finds himself in a rabbit hole he's unsure he can escape from when his movie receives the first ever R-rating.","genre_ids":[36,35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1008,"vote_count":7,"poster_path":"/zStGa4UxALdQ21Kr234VVL8fbXa.jpg","release_date":"2023-06-28","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"R","original_language":"en"},{"id":771,"adult":false,"title":"Home Alone","video":false,"overview":"Eight-year-old Kevin McCallister makes the most of the situation after his family unwittingly leaves him behind when they go on Christmas vacation. When thieves try to break into his home, he puts up a fight like no other.","genre_ids":[35,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8043,"vote_count":12309,"poster_path":"/i5We88HdO9Nsrv8xLyo4toNsLUM.jpg","release_date":"1990-11-16","vote_average":7.46,"backdrop_path":"/ih2xVgeMS8R5WUetYE8Mr9hVTlB.jpg","original_title":"Home Alone","original_language":"en"},{"id":238,"adult":false,"title":"The Godfather","video":false,"overview":"Spanning the years 1945 to 1955, a chronicle of the fictional Italian-American Corleone crime family. When organized crime family patriarch, Vito Corleone barely survives an attempt on his life, his youngest son, Michael steps in to take care of the would-be killers, launching a campaign of bloody revenge.","genre_ids":[18,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":36.9611,"vote_count":22508,"poster_path":"/3bhkrj58Vtu7enYsRolD1fZdja1.jpg","release_date":"1972-03-14","vote_average":8.687,"backdrop_path":"/tSPT36ZKlP2WVHJLM4cQPLSzv3b.jpg","original_title":"The Godfather","original_language":"en"},{"id":693134,"adult":false,"title":"Dune: Part Two","video":false,"overview":"Follow the mythic journey of Paul Atreides as he unites with Chani and the Fremen while on a path of revenge against the conspirators who destroyed his family. Facing a choice between the love of his life and the fate of the known universe, Paul endeavors to prevent a terrible future only he can foresee.","genre_ids":[878,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":22.2359,"vote_count":7552,"poster_path":"/1pdfLvkbY9ohJlCjQH2CZjjYVvJ.jpg","release_date":"2024-02-27","vote_average":8.13,"backdrop_path":"/ylkdrn23p3gQcHx7ukIfuy2CkTE.jpg","original_title":"Dune: Part Two","original_language":"en"},{"id":299534,"adult":false,"title":"Avengers: Endgame","video":false,"overview":"After the devastating events of Avengers: Infinity War, the universe is in ruins due to the efforts of the Mad Titan, Thanos. With the help of remaining allies, the Avengers must assemble once more in order to undo Thanos' actions and restore order to the universe once and for all, no matter what consequences may be in store.","genre_ids":[12,878,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":18.0537,"vote_count":27293,"poster_path":"/ulzhLuWrPK07P1YkdWQLZnQh1JL.jpg","release_date":"2019-04-24","vote_average":8.236,"backdrop_path":"/7RyHsO4yDXtBv1zUU3mTpHeQ0d5.jpg","original_title":"Avengers: Endgame","original_language":"en"},{"id":438631,"adult":false,"title":"Dune","video":false,"overview":"Paul Atreides, a brilliant and gifted young man born into a great destiny beyond his understanding, must travel to the most dangerous planet in the universe to ensure the future of his family and his people. As malevolent forces explode into conflict over the planet's exclusive supply of the most precious resource in existence-a commodity capable of unlocking humanity's greatest potential-only those who can conquer their fear will survive.","genre_ids":[878,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":18.3888,"vote_count":14483,"poster_path":"/d5NXSklXo0qyIYkgV94XAgMIckC.jpg","release_date":"2021-09-15","vote_average":7.778,"backdrop_path":"/wYMbnrdRCREjNLwFlG5SLWzBjui.jpg","original_title":"Dune","original_language":"en"},{"id":945961,"adult":false,"title":"Alien: Romulus","video":false,"overview":"While scavenging the deep ends of a derelict space station, a group of young space colonizers come face to face with the most terrifying life form in the universe.","genre_ids":[27,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":15.8348,"vote_count":4309,"poster_path":"/2uSWRTtCG336nuBiG8jOTEUKSy8.jpg","release_date":"2024-08-13","vote_average":7.169,"backdrop_path":"/iYqSQaWDttQIQzsxg9xHyg0bttG.jpg","original_title":"Alien: Romulus","original_language":"en"},{"id":617653,"adult":false,"title":"The Last Duel","video":false,"overview":"King Charles VI declares that Knight Jean de Carrouges settle his dispute with his squire, Jacques Le Gris, by challenging him to a duel.","genre_ids":[36,18,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.9442,"vote_count":3755,"poster_path":"/zjrJE0fpzPvX8saJXj8VNfcjBoU.jpg","release_date":"2021-10-13","vote_average":7.414,"backdrop_path":"/4LrL40XecjGLRpX5I2gzMTUt04l.jpg","original_title":"The Last Duel","original_language":"en"},{"id":11324,"adult":false,"title":"Shutter Island","video":false,"overview":"World War II soldier-turned-U.S. Marshal Teddy Daniels investigates the disappearance of a patient from a hospital for the criminally insane, but his efforts are compromised by troubling visions and a mysterious doctor.","genre_ids":[18,53,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":14.6244,"vote_count":25460,"poster_path":"/nrmXQ0zcZUL8jFLrakWc90IR8z9.jpg","release_date":"2010-02-14","vote_average":8.2,"backdrop_path":"/8xt8AMb1OKC63AdhNSaYBWxB4Iq.jpg","original_title":"Shutter Island","original_language":"en"},{"id":62,"adult":false,"title":"2001: A Space Odyssey","video":false,"overview":"Humanity finds a mysterious object buried beneath the lunar surface and sets off to find its origins with the help of HAL 9000, the world's most advanced super computer.","genre_ids":[878,9648,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":13.0323,"vote_count":12364,"poster_path":"/ve72VxNqjGM69Uky4WTo2bK6rfq.jpg","release_date":"1968-04-02","vote_average":8.056,"backdrop_path":"/w5IDXtifKntw0ajv2co7jFlTQDM.jpg","original_title":"2001: A Space Odyssey","original_language":"en"},{"id":653346,"adult":false,"title":"Kingdom of the Planet of the Apes","video":false,"overview":"Several generations following Caesar's reign, apes – now the dominant species – live harmoniously while humans have been reduced to living in the shadows. As a new tyrannical ape leader builds his empire, one young ape undertakes a harrowing journey that will cause him to question all he's known about the past and to make choices that will define a future for apes and humans alike.","genre_ids":[878,12,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":11.4341,"vote_count":4103,"poster_path":"/gKkl37BQuKTanygYQG1pyYgLVgf.jpg","release_date":"2024-05-08","vote_average":7.054,"backdrop_path":"/iHYh4cdO8ylA3W0dUxTDVdyJ5G9.jpg","original_title":"Kingdom of the Planet of the Apes","original_language":"en"},{"id":634649,"adult":false,"title":"Spider-Man: No Way Home","video":false,"overview":"Peter Parker is unmasked and no longer able to separate his normal life from the high-stakes of being a super-hero. When he asks for help from Doctor Strange the stakes become even more dangerous, forcing him to discover what it truly means to be Spider-Man.","genre_ids":[28,12,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":25.0407,"vote_count":21601,"poster_path":"/1g0dhYtq4irTY1GPXvft6k4YLjm.jpg","release_date":"2021-12-15","vote_average":7.932,"backdrop_path":"/nqUThBjou0TAWXu93Q4SNFpgqai.jpg","original_title":"Spider-Man: No Way Home","original_language":"en"},{"id":264660,"adult":false,"title":"Ex Machina","video":false,"overview":"Caleb, a coder at the world's largest internet company, wins a competition to spend a week at a private mountain retreat belonging to Nathan, the reclusive CEO of the company. But when Caleb arrives at the remote location he finds that he will have to participate in a strange and fascinating experiment in which he must interact