":"en"},{"id":471074,"adult":false,"title":"Connected","video":false,"overview":"\"Connected\" is a about two lonesome people who find each other via a chance encounter on a subway train. They experience happiness in one another for a brief moment in their lives until circumstances out of their control rip them apart. However their paths may once again intersect down the line.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"popularity":0.3412,"vote_count":9,"poster_path":"/tZtCpslgwRmRSleZIi0GmoWmaWH.jpg","release_date":"2008-04-08","vote_average":4.4,"backdrop_path":"/iLo62uzRS1YUDePTfvauOq8kE3R.jpg","original_title":"Connected","original_language":"en"},{"id":8391,"adult":false,"title":"When Night Is Falling","video":false,"overview":"Camille is a professor at a Protestant college and is in a long-term relationship with Martin, a respected minister and fellow professor. When Camille meets Petra, a bold and flamboyant performer in a circus troupe, she is inexplicably drawn. Pursuing Petra, Camille throws her whole conservative life into disarray.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.5971,"vote_count":88,"poster_path":"/6Ac5GLwJ01uli5mCXqXwquR36Y1.jpg","release_date":"1995-02-01","vote_average":6.261,"backdrop_path":"/5CCPKLWg0YWajQEXWYeY2w5c8qS.jpg","original_title":"When Night Is Falling","original_language":"en"},{"id":8436,"adult":false,"title":"The Page Turner","video":false,"overview":"Mélanie Prouvost, a ten-year-old butcher's daughter, is a gifted pianist. That is why she and her parents decide that she sit for the Conservatory entrance exam. Although Mélanie is very likely to be admitted, she unfortunately gets distracted by the president of the jury's offhand attitude and she fails. Ten years later, Mélanie becomes her page turner, waiting patiently for her revenge.","genre_ids":[18,10402,53],"popularity":0.4351,"vote_count":145,"poster_path":"/lBomGoLZKklJWb5hMvcy44WbUsd.jpg","release_date":"2006-08-09","vote_average":6.521,"backdrop_path":"/uyZMq9VTihrWBVXzIQUkB8P8Nnq.jpg","original_title":"La Tourneuse de pages","original_language":"fr"},{"id":661384,"adult":false,"title":"The Pier Man","video":false,"overview":"Theo is a young docker languishing in his native port. His life flows at the monotonous rhythm of cargo ships passing by. Through his encounter with Giuseppe, a disillusioned sailor ashore for a while, Theo will gather the courage to face the waves to escape his dull existence by trying to get into Giuseppe's gruff crew.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.1416,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/sC84npT8wSF1Nr9TE6x3R2eS1Ai.jpg","release_date":"2019-11-07","vote_average":1.8,"backdrop_path":"/x2fPXY8kkTjdki9yZsYtpA8vmmz.jpg","original_title":"L'homme jetée","original_language":"fr"},{"id":1067485,"adult":false,"title":"Sebastian","video":false,"overview":"Max is a 25-year-old freelance writer and aspiring novelist who seems well on his way to success in London’s cultural spheres. Yet by night, he finds a different kind of exhilaration as a sex worker with the pseudonym Sebastian, meeting men via an escorting platform. Max uses his experiences as Sebastian to fuel his stories and the worthy debut novel that he has been longing to write, finally seems within reach.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.2755,"vote_count":47,"poster_path":"/22JTGme2MLETmvhHQdiKP78S5Qf.jpg","release_date":"2024-08-02","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/kEvBFfqCtJvtvwZcrprAT3dSvij.jpg","original_title":"Sebastian","original_language":"en"},{"id":277436,"adult":false,"title":"Simon, el gran varón","video":false,"overview":"The first-born son of a wealthy Mexican businessman, Simon is doted upon by his father, Don Andres. But as Simon grows older, he displays a fondness for dressing in women's clothing and playing with dolls, and is eventually banished from home and disinherited. He then finds work as a performer in a nightclub that his father patronizes. Not recognizing his son as a beautiful young woman, Don Andres discloses some surprising secrets of his own.